name: Saved by the Barbell
description:
3 rounds for max reps of: 
•1 minute of burpees
•1 minute of wall-ball shots (20/14)
•1 minute of deadlifts (115/75)
•1 minute of med-ball sit-ups (20/14)
•1 minute of hang power cleans (115/75)
Rest 1 minute

This workout is an annual, world-wide CrossFit community Labor Day workout and fundraising effort to bring CrossFit to more kids everywhere. To find out more go to: https://crossfit.com/foundation/crossfitforkids
